The paper deals with the secretary problem, which is a classic problem in computer science and operations research. The paper specifically focuses on the problem over the intersection of several matroids, which is a topic in discrete optimization and combinatorial algorithms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
